 combination have a very damaging hit/effect upon the welfare of 
 producers in the developing (process of people making, selling, and buying things). For example, (one after the other) 
 oligopoly power combined with processor oligopsony power of 
 0.2 (Î¾ r = Î¾ w = Î¸ f = 0.2) combine to reduce producer extra 
 by about 49% relative to perfect competition in all downstream 
 parts/areas. 
